Upon failing a Skill Check, recieve a Boon from Dawn in exchange for losing 1 level in that Skill for the next day.

Condition of the Lost
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Whenever one is unable to find where to go for one reason or another, Dawn will offer a Boon in exhcange for an automatic Failiure on the next Navigation Check.

Condition of Fear
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Anytime one fails a Fear Check they gain a Boon from Dawn, in trade for a second Fear Check.